  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal set for Day 14 of the MONEY program: the day for naming what you are building for the people who come after you. Five prompts, around thirty minutes.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journal prompts as a practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "How do I feel about the week of work just completed?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write for five minutes. Name what shifted, what surprised you, what still feels uncertain.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What has already changed in how I think about money?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Name two or three concrete differences, in thought, in behaviour, or in how you respond.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What do I want my grandchildren to inherit from me around money?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Not just money itself, the beliefs, the habits, the relationship with earning and keeping. Be specific.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What is one thing I will do differently this week to build that legacy?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Concrete action, not intention. Something that can be done before the next prompt.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What belief do I want to carry forward into Week 3?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write one sentence. Finish this: \"I now choose to believe...\"",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Drawn from Day 14 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025). Also drawn from the Week 2 Reflection in The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom & Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
